1
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:35,980
♪Looking at the bright lights
of the long streets in my hometown♪

2
00:00:36,260 --> 00:00:39,480
♪I wrote down
that it's not too late to meet you♪

3
00:00:39,780 --> 00:00:45,260
♪Rereading it now,
I think it's just a joke in life♪

4
00:00:46,540 --> 00:00:49,580
♪During my beautiful youth,
I longed for peace♪

5
00:00:49,740 --> 00:00:53,240
♪I vowed to face challenges with you
before Buddha♪

6
00:00:53,940 --> 00:00:59,380
♪I pray to the gods not to be alone♪

7
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:03,140
♪Singing about farewell at Yang Pass♪

8
00:01:03,340 --> 00:01:06,300
♪Behind the sad song,
no one knows how I feel♪

9
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:13,100
♪Even though the streets are bustling,
I can only watch alone♪

10
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:16,500
♪Spend years on the sea,
drifting through foreign lands♪

11
00:01:16,780 --> 00:01:20,580
♪There have been
reunions and separations♪

12
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:26,300
♪There are countless sceneries,
none of them are half as good as you♪

13
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:30,180
♪I asked heaven and earth
where we can share the bright moon♪

14
00:01:30,420 --> 00:01:33,340
♪Looking back,
only the wind understands♪

15
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:39,980
♪Turns out that when love is deep,
right and wrong are forgotten♪

16
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:43,500
♪Let me ask you
how black hair turns white?♪

17
00:01:43,820 --> 00:01:47,180
♪I answer myself,
saying it's been a long separation♪

18
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:53,980
♪In the blink of an eye,
I lost my youthful appearance♪

19
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:04,680
=Cao Xuanxuan's Love Journey=

20
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:07,220
=Episode 2=

21
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,400
You tell me.

22
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,200
Is it possible...

23
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:17,040
That there could be two...

24
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,400
Two identical people.

25
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,680
It's possible.

26
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,800
Impressive.

27
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,860
That's how it's done.

28
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:43,040
Free rice!

29
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:44,040
Take a look.

30
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:45,240
I have no idea how to.

31
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,320
I can't do this.

32
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:48,880
- Can you do it?
- No.

33
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:50,200
This is amazing!

34
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,520
How is he so good at this?

35
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,200
It's done.

36
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:58,120
Great!

37
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,440
Make way.

38
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:07,920
What's your name?

39
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,320
I am Sun Weiyan.

40
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:10,600
Tell me.

41
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:11,760
How did you solve it?

42
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,720
What's so hard about it?

43
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:14,920
It's just

44
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,940
a toy similar to
children's building blocks.

45
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,080
When I was young,

46
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,240
I was skilled with such toys.

47
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:21,000
For example, the Kongming Lock,

48
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:22,080
the Nine Linked Rings,

49
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,200
and other similar puzzles.

50
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:33,920
How?

51
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:37,320
What do you mean?

52
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:38,760
The private secretary.

53
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:41,980
Not impressed.

54
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:42,720
Why not?

55
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:45,000
Why are you dissatisfied with me,
Magistrate Guo?

56
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,400
Look at him, he's so dashing.

57
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:49,420
He doesn't look like a proper person.

58
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,080
Besides,

59
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,840
even if he's good
at those silly puzzles,

60
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,680
he's not qualified
to be my private secretary.

61
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,360
In the Biography
of Confucius' Disciples,

62
00:03:56,380 --> 00:03:58,260
"Judging by appearance
overlooks true talent."

63
00:03:58,300 --> 00:03:58,960
Magistrate Guo,

64
00:03:58,960 --> 00:03:59,800
you must not do this.

65
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:02,280
You're just jealous
he's more handsome than you.

66
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,000
Step aside.

67
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,160
Are you

68
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:12,800
saying he's

69
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:14,600
more handsome than me?

70
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:16,160
You.

71
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,000
Leave here.

72
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,680
It's hard to find a true kindred spirit.

73
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,700
Since that's the case,

74
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:20,740
I shall take my leave.

75
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,200
Wait a moment.

76
00:04:23,340 --> 00:04:25,020
Strict gender barrier
must not be crossed.

77
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:25,960
Miss, behave yourself.

78
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:31,440
He doesn't
even appreciate your kindness.

79
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,680
Why are you keeping him?

80
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:34,360
He can solve a puzzle cube.

81
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,040
Can you?

82
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,340
One day of the five has gone by.

83
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,800
Tomorrow, we'll go to Zhao Village.

84
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,300
Besides him,

85
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,740
do you have any other candidates?

86
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,440
Becoming my private secretary

87
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:50,440
isn't entirely out of the question.

88
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,160
But I have to test you.

89
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,680
My private secretary

90
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:10,740
must possess profound knowledge
of both astronomy and geography,

91
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,560
which is beyond the reach
of ordinary people.

92
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:13,720
However,

93
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,760
I won't make it hard for you.

94
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,640
I'll ask you something simple.

95
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:20,400
Tell me, how many

96
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,200
men and women

97
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,200
are there in Yan City?

98
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,600
Guo Zijie,

99
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:27,920
you're running
a census just to mess with him!

100
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,360
You can't answer, can you?

101
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,360
If you can't, then get lost.

102
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,120
Don't waste my time.

103
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,000
Yan City oversees five towns

104
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,100
and twenty-three villages.

105
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,240
Men are counted as "ding".

106
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:38,480
Women are counted as "kou".

107
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:40,600
Each "ding" pays 20 coins annually
in taxes.

108
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,520
Each "kou" contributes 2 bolts
of cloth yearly.

109
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,500
Household registration records
may be incomplete.

110
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:45,930
But the imperial court collects taxes

111
00:05:45,940 --> 00:05:46,880
without exception.

112
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,600
Last year, taxes from "ding" amounted

113
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,440
to 1.8 million coins.

114
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:50,400
Taxes from "kou" totaled

115
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:51,320
220,000 bolts of cloth.

116
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,680
This corresponds to 90,000 men

117
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,920
and 110,000 women.

118
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,720
Nonsense.

119
00:06:12,860 --> 00:06:13,960
You've got some skills,

120
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,840
but I still need to test you again.

121
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,520
Just tell me,

122
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,320
how many cases

123
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,820
were reported in Yan City last year?

124
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:24,480
I don't know.

125
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,720
Guo Zijie, enough!

126
00:06:25,980 --> 00:06:27,020
Human lives are at stake.

127
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,520
Who has time to mess around with you?

128
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,860
If you don't want to use him,

129
00:06:29,900 --> 00:06:31,520
let Imperial Envoy
punish you instead!

130
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:35,920
Xuanxuan.

131
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,640
Fine, I'll use him, okay?

132
00:06:37,901 --> 00:06:40,620
(The Greatest Detective of Yan City)

133
00:06:42,300 --> 00:06:43,220
Young Master Sun,

134
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:44,400
please try this.

135
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,320
It's this spring's
pre-rain Longjing tea.

136
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:48,360
Our young master
only managed to get this much,

137
00:06:48,420 --> 00:06:49,620
and he's kept it all for you.

138
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,400
Good tea.

139
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,040
Off you go.

140
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,120
You...

141
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,200
Where did you get this thing?

142
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,760
I tinkered with it for ages

143
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:01,600
before I solved it.

144
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,040
That thing

145
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,480
is called

146
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,240
a Rubik's Cube.

147
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,320
A Rubik's Cube?

148
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,200
I've never heard of it.

149
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,080
But how did you remember it?

150
00:07:12,940 --> 00:07:14,560
I saw her demonstrate it once.

151
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,320
Just once?

152
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,420
No wonder people say you're smart.

153
00:07:18,860 --> 00:07:20,900
If it weren't for your fear
of your elder brother,

154
00:07:20,900 --> 00:07:22,520
you could have
earned an official title.

155
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:23,980
Why stay in this rundown Yan City

156
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,400
as a lowly official?

157
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,240
Zijie.

158
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:30,840
Zijie.

159
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:31,840
Ying?

160
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,320
Zijie.

161
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,280
Zijie,

162
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,800
try the pastries I just made.

163
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,240
Who are you?

164
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,040
I am Sun Weiyan,

165
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:46,240
the new private secretary
hired by Magistrate Guo.

166
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,680
Where's Zijie?

167
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,200
Magistrate Guo

168
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:52,520
went out for an inspection.

169
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,680
He ordered me

170
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,780
to organize the files here.

171
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,480
Really?

172
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:56,800
Miss,

173
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,840
you don't believe my words?

174
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,600
When Zijie comes back,

175
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,440
make sure to let him try

176
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,240
the pastries I made.

177
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:07,760
I put a lot of effort into them.

178
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:15,960
She's gone.

179
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:16,480
Come out.

180
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,040
That scared me.

181
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,040
Zijie,

182
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,920
is she the match Old Master Guo
arranged for you

183
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,120
after Cao Xuanxuan fell unconscious?

184
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,520
My father is getting old,

185
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:30,000
and having no heir is a grave matter,

186
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,680
so I agreed.

187
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,360
But recently, Xuanxuan woke up.

188
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,480
However, after she woke up,

189
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:37,460
her personality changed drastically,

190
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:40,000
and she's been messing
with all these strange little gadgets.

191
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:41,400
I'm wondering,

192
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:43,920
what if she was sent
by my elder brother?

193
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,280
That would be the end of me.

194
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:48,520
This Cao Xuanxuan saved your life,

195
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,440
so keeping her in the house is fine.

196
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,720
However,

197
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,680
given the current situation,

198
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,440
my greatest concern is

199
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,600
that your gratitude

200
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,870
might make you reluctant to act.

201
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:58,600
Zijie,

202
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,720
as an official,

203
00:08:59,920 --> 00:09:02,020
you must never
let compassion cloud your judgment.

204
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:03,480
I'll test her again.

205
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,720
I still don't trust her.

206
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,240
Leave this to me.

207
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:10,720
There's no need

208
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,580
for formalities between us.

209
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,880
Young Master Zilu,

210
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,600
I worked really hard

211
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,040
to get this for you.

212
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:25,200
What kind of useless thing is this?

213
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,840
I can't figure it out at all.

214
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,440
Young Master Zilu,

215
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:31,200
they recruited a private secretary

216
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,320
using this method.

217
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,320
They even hired a private secretary?

218
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:37,640
It's clear that they've been

219
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,200
steadily growing stronger.

220
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,400
Young Master Zilu,

221
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:42,120
what should we do now?

222
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:58,880
Understood, Young Master Zilu.

223
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,520
Grandpa,

224
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:07,560
try this.

225
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,480
I just learned it.

226
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,200
Good.

227
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:17,720
Who's there?

228
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,160
Mr. He,

229
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:21,660
Magistrate Guo requests your presence.

230
00:10:21,660 --> 00:10:22,500
Magistrate Guo?

231
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:23,880
All right.

232
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,480
Please wait at the entrance.

233
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:27,320
All right.

234
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,160
Chun,

235
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,080
bring me my case.

236
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:32,640
Go.

237
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,360
Grandpa,

238
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:52,360
can't you go after eating?

239
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,880
If Magistrate Guo is calling me,
it must be urgent.

240
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,560
I'll be back shortly.

241
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,080
Grandpa,

242
00:10:58,280 --> 00:11:00,160
why must you help that corrupt official?

243
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,240
Chun,

244
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,080
you're still young.

245
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:03,800
There are things

246
00:11:03,820 --> 00:11:04,900
you don't understand.

247
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:05,880
Magistrate Guo

248
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,640
is not a bad person.

249
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:13,880
Wait.

250
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:18,720
I'll go for you.

251
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:19,520
You?

252
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:20,640
Aren't you...

253
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:21,680
Grandpa,

254
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:22,960
your health isn't good.

255
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:23,800
Don't worry,

256
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:24,680
I can handle it.

257
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:28,840
Take care of yourself.

258
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,160
Help!

259
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,960
Kidnapping!

260
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,240
Help!

261
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:03,040
What's going on?

262
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,760
Something's off.

263
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,000
How could this happen?

264
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:02,440
Let go!

265
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:10,560
Xuanxuan.

266
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,080
He Chun?

267
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,120
Wait, Heroine!

268
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:38,400
Young Master Zilu.

269
00:13:38,540 --> 00:13:39,320
Young Master Zilu.

270
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,600
What is it?

271
00:13:40,700 --> 00:13:42,760
Why are you not sleeping
in the middle of the night?

272
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:43,680
What's the matter?

273
00:13:43,920 --> 00:13:44,640
Speak.

274
00:13:45,280 --> 00:13:47,000
The mission failed again.

275
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:48,640
Useless fool!

276
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:51,880
You can't even handle a simple task.

277
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,280
Young Master Zilu,

278
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:55,240
we followed your instructions exactly.

279
00:13:55,560 --> 00:13:57,340
We planned to abduct Cao Xuanxuan,

280
00:13:57,340 --> 00:13:59,320
keep her locked up for five days,
and release her.

281
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:00,300
Who knew...

282
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:02,280
a group of people would appear halfway,

283
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,720
and then a heroine would show up

284
00:14:03,800 --> 00:14:04,680
out of nowhere.

285
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:05,840
