579
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:56,520
what do you think?

580
00:29:57,360 --> 00:29:59,040
I think we should first investigate

581
00:29:59,040 --> 00:30:00,240
Fu Miao's social connections.

582
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:03,800
Social connections?

583
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:05,920
In other words,

584
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:08,440
bring in all the people
who frequently interacted with Fu Miao

585
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:09,740
and interrogate them one by one.

586
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:12,560
But there's no courtroom here.

587
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:14,940
How do we question them?

588
00:30:15,680 --> 00:30:17,140
An interrogation room.

589
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:18,360
Interrogation room?

590
00:30:19,320 --> 00:30:20,160
What room?

591
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:29,920
All right.

592
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:38,680
What is this contraption

593
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,160
good for?

594
00:30:40,360 --> 00:30:41,040
Interrogations.

595
00:30:42,320 --> 00:30:43,320
Studies show

596
00:30:43,560 --> 00:30:45,760
that people tend to feel drowsy
in dim environments.

597
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,120
The purpose of bright lights

598
00:30:47,320 --> 00:30:49,080
is to keep the suspect awake.

599
00:30:49,560 --> 00:30:50,880
Prolonged exposure to strong light

600
00:30:51,160 --> 00:30:52,560
can make people irritable,

601
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:54,020
which helps encourage suspects

602
00:30:54,120 --> 00:30:54,840
to confess.

603
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:57,560
This is unheard of.

604
00:30:58,340 --> 00:31:00,080
All right,
let's begin the interrogation.

605
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,040
Bring the first person in.

606
00:31:04,760 --> 00:31:05,320
Let's go.

607
00:31:12,160 --> 00:31:14,120
Greetings, Magistrate Guo.

608
00:31:14,180 --> 00:31:15,280
No need to bow. Please sit.

609
00:31:16,440 --> 00:31:18,200
I couldn't possibly.

610
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:19,000
Elder,

611
00:31:19,040 --> 00:31:20,320
there's no need to be nervous.

612
00:31:20,320 --> 00:31:21,860
We just have a few questions for you.

613
00:31:21,900 --> 00:31:23,660
Answer truthfully,
and you'll be free to go.

614
00:31:23,840 --> 00:31:24,740
Please, have a seat.

615
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:32,200
I heard that on the morning
after Fu Miao disappeared,

616
00:31:32,420 --> 00:31:33,680
you set fire on the mountain.

617
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:35,120
Sir,

618
00:31:35,800 --> 00:31:37,300
setting fire on the mountain

619
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:38,840
would bring divine punishment.

620
00:31:39,120 --> 00:31:39,800
I...

621
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:41,160
I wouldn't dare start a fire.

622
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:42,680
The one who set the fire was...

623
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:43,960
It was the fox spirit!

624
00:31:46,260 --> 00:31:47,520
What makes you say that?

625
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:48,720
Sir, you don't know.

626
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:50,800
When the villagers put out the fire,

627
00:31:50,800 --> 00:31:51,840
they found in the ashes

628
00:31:51,840 --> 00:31:52,920
a...

629
00:31:53,720 --> 00:31:54,840
A headscarf.

630
00:31:54,860 --> 00:31:55,940
What kind of headscarf?

631
00:31:56,320 --> 00:31:57,800
The kind scholars wear.

632
00:31:58,080 --> 00:31:59,280
I heard the scholars call it

633
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:01,440
a scholar's cap.

634
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:02,480
A scholar's cap?

635
00:32:02,560 --> 00:32:04,200
What does this scholar's cap look like?

636
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:06,320
What else could it look like?

637
00:32:06,320 --> 00:32:07,480
It's what scholars wear.

638
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:09,440
My husband...

639
00:32:11,760 --> 00:32:12,600
In our village,

640
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:14,240
there are plenty of men to marry.

641
00:32:14,360 --> 00:32:15,640
Why did you insist on taking in

642
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:16,800
a scholar from another place?

643
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:17,680
He...

644
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:20,120
He ate the offspring
of the Fox Spirit Empress.

645
00:32:20,360 --> 00:32:21,420
The Fox Spirit Empress

646
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:23,220
dragged him
into the mountains and burned him

647
00:32:23,220 --> 00:32:24,400
as a sacrifice for her cubs.

648
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:25,520
If this matter

649
00:32:25,800 --> 00:32:27,800
ends here, so be it.

650
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:28,520
But if

651
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:29,880
it implicates our village,

652
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:32,040
it will be your fault!

653
00:32:32,320 --> 00:32:32,680
Enough.

654
00:32:32,840 --> 00:32:33,620
You're done here.

655
00:32:33,800 --> 00:32:34,280
Leave.

656
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:40,640
It's all because of you!

657
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,720
This is your fault!

658
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:43,120
It's all because of you!

659
00:32:45,440 --> 00:32:46,600
It's because of you!

660
00:32:46,600 --> 00:32:47,920
It's your fault!

661
00:32:49,120 --> 00:32:50,080
It's all your doing!

662
00:32:50,080 --> 00:32:50,840
Silence!

663
00:32:51,560 --> 00:32:52,560
The magistrate is here.

664
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:53,680
No disorderly conduct.

665
00:32:54,840 --> 00:32:56,240
This thing of yours is too strange.

666
00:32:56,400 --> 00:32:57,500
Look how agitated he is.

667
00:33:00,080 --> 00:33:01,320
Everyone, listen to me.

668
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:03,560
I'm certain there's no
such thing as a fox spirit.

669
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:05,760
Everything that's happened
is the work of humans.

670
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:07,640
You can't say things
like that recklessly!

671
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:09,320
The gods are watching from above.

672
00:33:09,320 --> 00:33:10,760
Don't let the fox spirit hear you.

673
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:11,960
What's she afraid of?

674
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:13,540
If Fox Spirit Empress gets angry,

675
00:33:13,560 --> 00:33:14,920
it's us villagers who will suffer.

676
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:15,600
Right?

677
00:33:15,600 --> 00:33:16,320
Grab her!

678
00:33:16,480 --> 00:33:17,080
Yes!

679
00:33:17,080 --> 00:33:18,420
We'll be the ones who pay for it!

680
00:33:18,420 --> 00:33:19,520
Yes! Don't let her escape.

681
00:33:19,520 --> 00:33:20,480
She can't leave!

682
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:21,040
Right!

683
00:33:21,120 --> 00:33:22,440
Tie her up!

684
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:23,520
Don't let her leave!

685
00:33:24,160 --> 00:33:24,640
Enough!

686
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:27,640
I'm here to get to the bottom of this.

687
00:33:27,820 --> 00:33:29,840
I'll give you all a proper explanation.

688
00:33:30,080 --> 00:33:30,760
Sir!

689
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:31,840
Sir!

690
00:33:32,040 --> 00:33:33,280
We've found Fu Miao's body.

691
00:33:34,560 --> 00:33:35,280
You've found it?

692
00:33:35,340 --> 00:33:36,280
Let's go take a look.

693
00:33:36,320 --> 00:33:37,420
- Let's go!
- Let's go!

694
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:41,560
Excuse me.

695
00:33:59,560 --> 00:34:01,200
Dear!

696
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:06,040
Dear!

697
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:10,080
Dear!

698
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:13,120
He Chun!

699
00:34:15,200 --> 00:34:16,360
Dear!

700
00:34:17,120 --> 00:34:18,040
Xiaolin,

701
00:34:18,640 --> 00:34:19,520
don't be too upset.

702
00:34:19,540 --> 00:34:21,080
Let them examine what happened first.

703
00:34:57,680 --> 00:34:59,240
The body is already bloated and decayed.

704
00:34:59,560 --> 00:35:01,080
There's noticeable swelling

705
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:02,520
in the throat and wrists,

706
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:03,920
more than in the other areas.

707
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:06,320
The time of death

708
00:35:06,900 --> 00:35:08,520
should have been about four days ago.

709
00:35:08,520 --> 00:35:09,680
After the murder,

710
00:35:09,680 --> 00:35:11,520
the killer should have
set the body on fire,

711
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:13,760
not drowned it in the pond.

712
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:50,760
♪Like the setting sun,
which repeatedly sets in the west♪

713
00:35:52,020 --> 00:35:57,460
♪My heart goes over mountains
to rest with you♪

714
00:35:58,620 --> 00:36:02,060
♪As the winds and clouds shift,
our encounter♪

715
00:36:02,060 --> 00:36:05,820
♪Seems like the perfect foreshadowing♪

716
00:36:06,220 --> 00:36:11,260
♪But it was a misplaced expectation♪

717
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:15,860
♪I think I'm exceptionally affectionate♪

718
00:36:16,060 --> 00:36:18,980
♪Devotion can warm the coldest ice♪

719
00:36:19,340 --> 00:36:22,540
♪And you're a shooting star
that flashes by♪

720
00:36:22,980 --> 00:36:25,260
♪Out of reach♪

721
00:36:26,340 --> 00:36:29,540
♪I prayed for a miracle countless times♪

722
00:36:29,820 --> 00:36:33,940
♪If I meet you, I only wish
we could be together forever♪

723
00:36:34,220 --> 00:36:40,340
♪But only the distant phantom remains♪

724
00:36:40,460 --> 00:36:43,500
♪Love rises like the wind
but remains unsettled when it stops♪

725
00:36:43,780 --> 00:36:46,780
♪Chasing you through four seasons,
wandering for a lifetime♪

726
00:36:47,060 --> 00:36:48,740
♪Fish in the water♪

727
00:36:48,740 --> 00:36:53,980
♪Is greedy for the reflection
of clouds in the heart of the lake♪

728
00:36:54,180 --> 00:36:57,100
♪From dusk to dawn,
from heavy snow to early clear sky♪

729
00:36:57,300 --> 00:37:01,620
♪Searching for your footprints
from south to west♪

730
00:37:01,980 --> 00:37:07,620
♪The wind stops,
but the dream isn't over♪
